 MBOMBELA – MBOMBELA – Mr and Ms Hoërskool Bergvlam 2019 were crowned amid much fanfare in a packed school hall last Wednesday evening. After an entertaining evening and a programme which included dramatic performances, Jason van den Heever and Bonolo Ranalana were crowned as this year’s Mr and Ms Bergvlam. ALSO READ: Pumas ask high court to red card ISG The school rolled out the red carpet for the 20 finalists and loud cheers echoed through the hall from friends and fans as the hopefuls walked the runway.